aa(lp57
VAnd here is another example
p58
aVof a parasitic manipulation.
p59
aVThis is a suicidal cricket.
p60
aVThis cricket swallowed the  larvae of a Gordian worm,
p61
aVor horsehair worm.
p62
aVThe worm grew to adult size within it,
p63
aVbut it needs to get into water in order to mate,
p64
aVand it does that by releasing proteins
p65
aVthat addle the cricket's brain,
p66
aVcausing it to behave erratically.
