aa(lp74
VThe tapeworm and the Gordian worm are not alone.
p75
aVThey are part of an entire cavalcade
p76
aVof mind-controlling parasites,
p77
aVof fungi, viruses, and worms and insects and more
p78
aVthat all specialize in subverting and overriding
